room_title: Escape room "C-Block" by Escape Experience Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: I assumed when I first went this would be at least a LITTLE lame. I couldn't have been more wrong. Loved it, went back and loved it again. All 3 experiences are challenging and very fun, and when the next one opens, I'll be in for that one too. Outstanding experience.

room_title: Escape room "C-Block" by Escape Experience Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: My friends and I tried to escape the vaccine room. We ran into a snag because one of the locks were placed incorrectly, but it was still a blast and I highly recommend it. I dropped a star because because of the incorrectly placed lock. There will absolutely be a rematch if I'm ever in Chattanooga again!
